Sanofi U.S. - Sanofi US researches, develops and brings to market new and innovative healthcare products and treatments for cardiovascular diseases, oncology, sleep disorder, thrombosis, allergy and respiratory illness, diabetes, central nervous system, internal medicine, metabolic disorders, osteoporosis and hypertension.





































