Sanofi

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Sanofi S.A.





Type

Société Anonyme


Traded as
Euronext: SAN
NYSE: SNY
CAC 40 Component


Industry
Pharmaceuticals


Founded
20 August 2004 (by acquisition) as Sanofi Aventis
6 May 2011 as Sanofi


Headquarters
54, Rue La Boétie, 75008 Paris, France



Area served

